  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42744</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_058_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたし……あの人のこと、
許せないよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I will never forgive him for what he's done!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42824</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_058_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あの人って……バジルさん？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Him...? You mean Basil?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42892</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_058_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuruuruuu!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42980</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_058_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……最後の最後に&lt;Dio&gt;を傷つけて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't want to see &lt;Dio&gt; depressed...I hope he's never hurt like this ever again...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43092</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_058_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>かもしれない。でも、バジルさんは、
もう死んじゃったんだよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I hope for the same... But he really does believe in Basil, didn't he?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43220</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_058_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だからよけいに許せないの。怒れる相手が
もういなくて、怒る意味ないから……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't care! I won't forgive him! There's no reason to make someone drown in their sorrow this much...No reason...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43340</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_058_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だったらわかってるでしょ。
許せないって言ってもどうしようもないこと</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I understand perfectly. But we shouldn't hold grudges against people.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43444</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_058_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そう……だよね……
でも、気持ちがおさまらなくて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's true but...I can't give closure to these feelings...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_058_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それはわかるけド……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I understand but...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43652</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_058_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>今は傷ついた&lt;Dio&gt;をなんとかすることでしか、
それをおさめることはできないと思うんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Right now we should only worry about &lt;Dio&gt; and be close to him. Negativity will only make things worse.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43712</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_058_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Right.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43816</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_058_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ぼくだって……
許せない気持ち、&lt;Mel&gt;と同じだよ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Though, to be frank... I feel the same. I don't think I'll ever forgive him...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
